reviewText: The video didn't play at all. Was damaged when I got it. Very disappointed. I did get a refund though so I was glad of that!
LOVE THESE STORIES, LOVE GOLDEN BOOK VIDEOS, BUT I DIDNT LIKE THAT THEY DIDNT MOVE THEIR LIPS. THIS VIDEO IS GREAT OTHER THAN IT BEING STILL PICTURES WITH JUST VOICES
My daughter loved these when she was a little girl, so I had to purchase them for my granddaughter.
